            {
                "comment": "Lectures are really required discussions since all the lectures are videos online. A quiz is taken in every discussion on the videos before we've even discussed them. You have to watch more videos for lab, and there are online quizzes too. The labs were the high point of this class, actually kind of fun. Lab reports take a long time.",
